OL,3,CFuneral held for fatally stabbed
OL,4,Cteenager Mason Rist
OL,6,FThe funeral of a teenager stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath in Bristol was held today
OL,8,F(Friday 22 March).
OL,10,FPeople gathered in Knowle West to
OL,11,Fcelebrate the life of Mason Rist, 15,
OL,12,Fwho was killed along with his friend
OL,13,FMax Dixon, 16, in January 2024.
OL,15,FEscorting the 15-year-old on his final
OL,16,Fjourney was his family, dressed in the
OL,17,FLiverpool kit - to honour their
OL,18,Ffootball-loving teenager.
