OL,6,FEvery seat was taken inside Knowle
OL,7,FMethodist Church. Those that couldn't
OL,8,Fsit, stood outside.
OL,10,FA community united in grief
OL,12,FRev Sally Spencer said: "Mason was
OL,13,Fclearly a child and a young man and he
OL,14,Fwas secure in the love of his family,
OL,15,Fwho had good friends and who knew what
OL,16,Fhe liked and who he was.
OL,18,F"There were three things that Mason
OL,19,Fparticularly liked - his play station,
OL,20,Fsports cars, and Liverpool FC."
