OL,3,CFuneral held for fatally stabbed
OL,4,Cteenager Mason Rist
OL,6,FMason Rist and his 16 year old best
OL,7,Ffriend Max Dixon were stabbed to death
OL,8,Fnear their home in Knowle West at the
OL,9,Fend of January.
OL,11,F"I miss you so much"
OL,13,FChloe Rist, Mason's sister, said: "No
OL,14,Fone could make me cry with laughter
OL,15,Fand belly-laugh like he could.
OL,17,F"He was so entertaining to be around,
OL,18,Fand I always knew my time with him was
OL,19,Fprecious.
