OL,3,CFuneral held for fatally stabbed
OL,4,Cteenager Mason Rist
OL,6,F"I am grateful to have 15 good years
OL,7,Fwith him, and I know you're safe now,
OL,8,Fwith your best friend Max.
OL,10,F"You will always have a special place
OL,11,Fin our hearts, and we thank you for
OL,12,Fbeing you and for all the amazing
OL,13,Ftimes you gave us."
OL,15,FRoss Rist, his brother, said: "We will
OL,16,Fmeet again one day, I miss you so much
OL,17,Flittle bro."
OL,19,FFor a boy who loved Liverpool, their
OL,20,Fanthem 'You'll Never Walk Alone' was a
OL,21,Ffitting tribute to end the service.
