OL,6,FTo honour Mason, white doves were
OL,7,Freleased - a symbol of hope and peace
OL,8,F- for a community which has suffered
OL,9,Fso much pain.
OL,11,FOn Thursday 21 March a private funeral
OL,12,Ffor Max Dixon was held South Bristol
OL,13,FCrematorium.
